                     <interp inst="t18340220-187-person1768" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I saw the prisoner take the trousers and run away with them - we pursued and took him.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340220-187-person1769">
                  WILLIAM 
